Scope notes (not binding, informational):

- This license covers all source code in this repository, including the
  CloudFlare Worker indexer (`game/indexer/`), the PartyKit / CF relay
  (`game/cf-relay/`, `game/partykit-probe/`), the companion UI
  (`companion/`), and any ES modules published under `game/pbrp/`,
  `game/signin-verify.mjs`.

- The `game/` directory is gitignored by default (the Pokemon ROM and
  IP-derived artifacts live there), with explicit whitelist for the
  open-source infrastructure subdirectories. See `.gitignore`.

- Pokemon franchise trademarks, sprites, ROM assets, and in-game content
  remain the property of Nintendo, Game Freak, and Creatures Inc. This
  license does NOT grant any rights over Pokemon intellectual property.
  The indexer code is generic Bells ordinals tooling; it happens to be
  used for a Pokemon-themed on-chain game but is not derived from
  Nintendo assets.

- Contributors to the PokeBells protocol schemas (`p:pokebells`,
  `p:pokebells-manifest`, `p:pokebells-sprites`, `p:pokebells-collection`)
  license their schema contributions under the same MIT terms. Schema
  locks (see `memory/schema_v14_commit_reveal.md` +
  `memory/mainnet_lockin_architecture.md`) happen pre-mainnet mint.
